    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“It's kind of wild nobody elaborated on his research in the last 82 years, you'd think someone would at least check up on the place”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257190/extras/ffe15b5a23a4048ca4d28719717655e0.avif?t=1729027047\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257190/extras_big/ffe15b5a23a4048ca4d28719717655e0.avif?t=1729027047 width=800 height=253 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>explore the world</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For Old Time's Sake is a semi open world detective role-playing game. Set in a solarpunk near future world, made to be an ideal for a bright future. Follow the story of Archie as you explore, do quests, find secrets and solve the mystery.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>scoot around!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257190/extras/c56ddbc1cb8069b10ac6f4bee74cb797.poster.avif?t=1729027047\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257190/extras/c56ddbc1cb8069b10ac6f4bee74cb797.webm?t=1729027047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257190/extras/c56ddbc1cb8069b10ac6f4bee74cb797.mp4?t=1729027047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>use gadgets and devices</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257190/extras/37f6c5df9aa7678a41b08aa5013d84e5.poster.avif?t=1729027047\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257190/extras/37f6c5df9aa7678a41b08aa5013d84e5.webm?t=1729027047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257190/extras/37f6c5df9aa7678a41b08aa5013d84e5.mp4?t=1729027047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A charming hand drawn artstyle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a rich world to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >many npc's</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a thrilling story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >fun movement mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a plucky trans woman who can double jump</p></li></ul>",
